title: Quantitative Trading and Market Making with Sam Trabucco: Episode 12
description: Will Clemente and Alameda Research CEO/Quant trader Sam Trabucco discuss what's going on in the Bitcoin market, quantitative trading, market making, and more for our weekly interview Podcast/YouTube channel series. Can now find our podcast on Spotify, Apple, and Google Podcasts as well!  Sam's twitter: twitter.com/AlamedaTrabucco
